Hiebert: National
Geographic's relationship

00:00:36.168 --> 00:00:40.173 line:0%
with photography and
Peru are all intertwined.

00:00:41.941 --> 00:00:42.875 line:0%
All of Peru,

00:00:43.009 --> 00:00:46.779 line:0%
unbelievable country
of mysteries and surprises.

00:00:46.779 --> 00:00:49.916 line:0%
This is definitely one of
the centers of civilization.

00:00:50.917 --> 00:00:53.218 line:0%
It's really
incredible to be able

00:00:53.218 --> 00:00:56.189 line:0%
to look into the eyes
of an ancient ruler.

00:00:56.189 --> 00:00:59.025
This is the power
of archaeology.

